txt.en: Hunt the Wargs that harass travellers in the Eastern Bruinen Source portion of the Misty Mountains.
Wargs stalk the drifts in the Misty Mountains, north and east of Rivendell, near the ridges of Pinnath Fenui.\n\nDefeat the Wargs that stalk the mountains.
Wargs stalk the drifts in the Misty Mountains, north and east of Rivendell, near the ridges of Pinnath Fenui.\n\nDefeat the Wargs that stalk the mountains.
'I am glad you were so successful from your hunt, [placeholder]! Wargs are dangerous prey, and you have slain many!'
Vighar Roadwalker is located in a camp at the High Crag.\n\nVighar will be pleased to hear that you have lessened the menace of the Wargs that stalk the Misty Mountains.

'Goblins use the Wargs for tracking and hunting, and the creatures guard the outskirts of goblin-encampments. Best to slaughter them all. Look for them far to the east, near the ridges of Pinnath Fenui.'
'The Wargs of Pinnath Fenui have been a great worry since we came to this place.'
'The goblins and the Wargs are close allies, and a great trouble to us.'
'Thank you for your aid, [placeholder]. The Wargs are more wary than they were.'
